By the amazing @kujo_kev

we buried my only big brother reggie saturday , he was hit by an uber driver at 3am and passed away in the morning. Every moment in my life he’s been there, he was first friend, first roomate, first inspiration and first protector. I’ll miss him dearly. I hesitated posting this because i usually like to keep my personal life personal but i decided to share because Tour starts in two weeks and I just wanna tell folks to be a bit more patient with me as, and if i seem distant, quiet or stand offish i promise it isn’t you, it’s just me thinking of my big brother reggie. Thank you to all the friends and extended family for your messages , illl see you soon big brother but first i got some work to do❤️
